{"tid":1498994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"慎防[納粹屠殺 / 大清洗] 食飯聽到老人V7指內地親戚分享支持民族大清洗港獨","createTime":"2019-08-23T14:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T20:16:01.000Z","uid":294333,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bd05275c1e02acc5b8c2eb5654a7460fecda8cc2","tid":1498994,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"唉，<br />\n尋晚起街食飯，<br />\n鄰近6-70歲老人家電話收到 大陸親威V7分享，部電話勁大聲播出黎<br />\n內容話香港恐怖份子太過分，沒有中國接收香港領土，就沒有今天香港繁榮，仲係英奴，今日竟然反抗國家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後佢電話播v7 D 親戚錄音訊息，部電話勁大聲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n將港毒 進行種族大清洗，派老解屠城，炸爛到香港陸沉就最好，再收回香港二次回歸，14億中華兒女不需要香港人</span></strong><br />\n</span></strong></strong></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">然後個老人家好激動，錄音V7反駁佢個大陸親威，忘恩負義，係當年大陸大飢荒時，佢一蘿蘿豉油，食油，罐頭運返大陸，又寄錢返娜下救濟。華南大水災，四川大地震香港人捐勁撚多錢返去，香港人投資幾咁多錢開廠，你地又咁鍾意落黎香港買藥品奶粉，係咪傻撚西左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勁CLS，大陸乜乜主播視頻國家級宣傳 種族仇恨，肅反運動抬頭，民粹主義，香港人不能輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c024e5146031d97c9cf362c3e9ff1d763b162630","tid":1498994,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=84c88fcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n全能既香港人連一份簽名都完成唔到？"},{"pid":"caa94e1ac81cc53534b7595f6f29e703b0da65f0","tid":1498994,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:48:08.000Z","msg":"試下 十幾萬美國人喺度"},{"pid":"49bdf1afc9821528b9b59894819c3bf6c1e5c86e","tid":1498994,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"呢班中國狗先應該被清洗<br />\n身為社會底層竟然當自己係統治者 笑死人"},{"pid":"5da609ae10cd5874cf51e52d58e3b2bd566c1a31","tid":1498994,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"721, 811"},{"pid":"60607464ac0f717e869eb6a853875054da6124f7","tid":1498994,"uid":267348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"陸沉仲收咩香港阿，係水底啦"},{"pid":"ae185cdcac436e2084bc7002f23a5eb03c522698","tid":1498994,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60un76F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60un76F.jpg&h=876ef65c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"924483590b7386ea0c95e0fcc3b34211e86928d3","tid":1498994,"uid":201356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"caa94e1ac81cc53534b7595f6f29e703b0da65f0","tid":1498994,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:48:08.000Z","msg":"試下 十幾萬美國人喺度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"唔使靠美國人 我哋自然會守護我城<br />\n香港人咁多日已經證明自己做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab79db793769190dba8f718ff75de7e839b9878f","tid":1498994,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606074